<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08079</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT RECONSTITUTING THE GOVERNING BOARD OF THE PHILIPPINE COCONUT AUTHORITY (PCA)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Aims to reconstitute the PCA Board that shall manage the Coconut Farmers and Industry Development Trust Fund.
Authorizes the PCA to implement a reorganization plan to increase its personnel complement with a dedicated unit for planning, evaluation of proposals and monitoring of the proposals and projects funded by the Coconut Farmers and Industry Development Trust Fund. 
</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>PANGANIBAN, JOSE JR. T. CPA, LLB, MACAPAGAL ARROYO, GLORIA, YAP, ARTHUR C., LAGMAN, EDCEL C., LOBREGAT, CELSO L., SAGARBARRIA, MANUEL, ESCUDERO, EVELINA G., TAN, ANGELINA &quot;HELEN&quot; D.L. M.D., CHAVEZ, CECILIA LEONILA V., SUAREZ, DANILO E.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-08-08</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Sy-Alvarado (000 2018-09-06)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>MOTHER BILL:&nbspHB08552</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON GOVERNMENT ENTERPRISES AND PRIVATIZATION ON 2018-08-14</td></tr></table>